raking, or friction products. It appears that Midas\'92 own retail outlets operate on a franchise basis with the franchisees free to purchase their supplies from the franchisor, Midas, or to give their business to an independent supplier.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s12{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs66\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 Midas naturally supplies both its own retail franchisees as well as other independent retailers.}}}
