{\*\cs66\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af10\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af10\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177\rtlch\af8\ltrch\hich\f8\loch\f8 }{\rtlch\af8\ltrch\hich\f8\loch\f8  (\'93van der Bijl\'94) This was not a happy time for Erasmus.  He felt his entrepreneurial style cramped by the requirements 
